[PDF] Anegudde Sri Vinayaka Temple | Anegudde Temple | Kumbashi | Kundapura
Itslife.in
“Ane” means Elephant and “Gudde” means hill, hence the temple is atop a hill. This temple is one of the seven of Lord Parashurama Kshetras / pilgrim center.
